spec_data.Name: pssh
spec_data.Description:
This package provides various parallel tools based on ssh and scp.
Parallell version includes:
 o ssh : pssh
 o scp : pscp
 o nuke : pnuke
 o rsync : prsync
 o slurp : pslurp
